			<body><h2><strong>Actors, Actions and Requirements.</strong></h2>
<p><strong>1. Users : </strong>The person who wants to book a ticket(s) for a show.</p>
<ul>
<li>Registration.</li>
<li>City Selection.</li>
<li>Search/ select a category of interest.</li>
<li>Search for shows and reviews.</li>
<li>Language of interest.</li>
<li>Search for the show(date, time, theater).</li>
<li>Seat selection.</li>
<li>Food options selection.</li>
<li>Make payment.</li>
<li>notification method selection.</li>
<li>ticket Cancellation request.</li>
<li>Submit Reviews and Ratings.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>2. Theater Manager: </strong>Theaters, Auditorium, and stadiums who want to bring there show on the BookMyShow platform.</p>
<ul>
<li>Registration.</li>
<li>Create shows(Add movie, Select City, theaters, and Timing).</li>
<li>Provide Movies and Actors info.</li>
<li>Provide Seating arrangements and pricing.</li>
<li>Add amenities info.</li>
<li>Payments.</li>
<li>Refunds.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>3.BookMyShow System  Admin: (Person who Adds new events, shows, cities, and genres on the platform.)</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Verify the Users.</li>
<li>Add new cities.</li>
<li>Add new theaters.</li>
<li>Add a new Category/genre.</li>
<li>add offers.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>4. System &#40;BookMyShow Platform&#41;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Collect the users' info for verification.</li>
<li>Recommend movies.</li>
<li>Process Payments.</li>
<li>Process cancellations and refunds.</li>
<li>Send notifications.</li>
<li>display movie titles and reviews.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p></body></html>